          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The helium generation materials",
                "included eleven Al, Fe, Ni, Cu, and Au pure-element",
                "helium accumulation dosimetry wire rings, oriented",
                "concentrically with the irradiation capsule axis. The",
                "helium accumulation dosimetry rings from the",
                "irradiated capsule were etched, segmented, weighted,",
                "and analyzed for generated helium using a",
                "high-sensitivity gas mass spectrometer."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The helium concentrations measured for the helium",
                "accumulation ring segments were then used to",
                "calculated relative helium generation cross sections.",
                "To calculate them, the helium measurements were",
                "normalized using the spectrum- integrated fluence",
                "profiles, estimated to have +-10% uncertainties. The",
                "profiles were integrated over the finite source",
                "geometry, for neutron energies above 5 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
